India Officials to Meet Tomorrow on Borrowing Plan, Gopalan Says

-- B y   K a r t i k   G o y a l
-- 
2011-09-28T05:09:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/india-officials-to-meet-tomorrow-on-borrowing-plan-gopalan-says.html
Officials from  India ’s finance
ministry and the central bank will meet tomorrow to decide on
the federal government’s borrowing plan for the six months
starting Oct. 1,  R. Gopalan, economic affairs secretary in the
finance ministry, said in  New Delhi  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
